==Annotations==
'''Nebrakada! Feminimum!'''{{spaces|5}}See [[Annotations_to_James_Joyce%27s_Ulysses/Wandering_Rocks/233|233.08]]. Gabler corrects the spelling of the second word to '''Femininum''', which is the form Stephen reads at 233.08, but he does not restore the italics.

