==Annotations==
'''''bona fides'''''{{spaces|5}}(''Latin'') ''good faith''. In English, ''[[wikt:bona fides|bona fides]]'' means ''sincerity'' or ''trustworthiness'', particularly in relation to a person's stated identity.

