==Annotations==
'''''passim'''''{{spaces|5}}(''Latin'') ''here and there''. In English, ''[[wikt:passim|passim]]'' is often used in conjunction with the name of a book or writer to indicate that a word, a phrase or an idea is to be found at many places in the writer's work — too many for them to be individually enumerated.


